Program: Discovery
Title: Impossible Visions - exploring the atom
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry8v
Last Broadcast Date: 03 December 2002
Exploring the world of the atom and the history behind its discovery. The final in the series looks at how we are able to view some of the smallest particles in the universe. However even atoms are not quite the smallest objects that exist.